{"tid":1393653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[喜訊] 新登記選民逾38萬人　廿歲以下新選民最多","createTime":"2019-08-01T07:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:47:15.000Z","uid":260950,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3218ad70a65238e47e583cfc56c34bd863129754","tid":1393653,"uid":260950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】選舉事務處公布臨時選民登記冊，新登記選民達38萬6千人。<br />\n<br />\n2019年地方選區臨時選民登記冊，有近412萬選民，約38萬6千為新登記選民，當中18至20歲新登記選民有五萬八千人，是所有年齡組別中選民增加人數最多；其次是31至35歲，有四萬六千多名新登記選民。<br />\n<br />\n今次是選民登記冊首次突破400萬人，而新登記選民的增加人數亦是回歸以來最多。<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處呼籲市民在本月25日前，上網查閱最新登記資料，而正式選民登記冊會在下月25日前公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=357551&amp;fbclid=IwAR0eYd5vhfnYLLGCTTL-hpipTKSqx9TSDCMeRA0MNTUE1fawQCQ015K52kM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357551%26fbclid%3DIwAR0eYd5vhfnYLLGCTTL-hpipTKSqx9TSDCMeRA0MNTUE1fawQCQ015K52kM&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl55hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=cc8fe32b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357551%26fbclid%3DIwAR0eYd5vhfnYLLGCTTL-hpipTKSqx9TSDCMeRA0MNTUE1fawQCQ015K52kM&h=e99ba072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=357551&amp;fbclid=IwAR0eYd5vhfnYLLGCTTL-hpipTKSqx9TSDCMeRA0MNTUE1fawQCQ015K52kM</a>"},{"pid":"a845c72dd733f634e91de0de90524fcf874ce61b","tid":1393653,"uid":107216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"您老味，建制死出香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5784c92743ad7dcb277b41e336ff0e91599e5ae7","tid":1393653,"uid":90601,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:12:45.000Z","msg":"18至20有成5萬人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.g